Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.94,0:56:42.04,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好似划破夜空的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.33,0:56:46.44,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无时无刻 渲染着哀愁
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.71,0:56:55.40,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}如同在述说真实
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.84,0:57:04.12,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,200)}熟悉的景色 碎作残片
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.28,0:57:08.47,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一片片映出哭泣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.69,0:57:12.96,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温馨的记忆中
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.16,0:57:25.50,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只手相牵…Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.66,0:57:30.07,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}放飞思念 描绘螺旋
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.27,0:57:34.35,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}舞出我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.50,0:57:38.66,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊 倾听灵魂的细语 声声鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.83,0:57:43.04,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}活在同一个时空
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.23,0:57:47.72,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}放声大喊 即便遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.91,0:57:51.97,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}必能传达到你心中
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.15,0:57:56.30,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}转呀转 这里无边无垠
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.44,0:58:05.65,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}黑暗中仰望同一片梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.22,0:58:23.39,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,200)}善良不是救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.62,0:58:27.73,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在充满矛盾的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.01,0:58:32.21,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果未与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.44,0:58:44.70,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我甚至不识自己的孤独…Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.90,0:58:47.09,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愿望张开翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.30,0:58:49.28,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如同奏起永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.41,0:58:53.53,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}乘风翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.73,0:58:57.91,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊 寻求光明 那张侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.11,0:59:02.40,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与你共同仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.57,0:59:04.77,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}挣扎在命运的漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.92,0:59:06.92,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.08,0:59:11.11,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}再不折返 直面梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.29,0:59:15.63,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}盛起滴落的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.81,0:59:25.19,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}期待同一轮破晓的旭日


